          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-13-1692964119530-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the <strong>spicy peanut sauce</strong> and<strong> drained noodles </strong>to the pan and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>spicy peanut chicken noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the reserved starchy noodle water if it's looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-12-1692964145591-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-12-1692964145591-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-12-1692964145591-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-12-1692964145591-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
